name: Startuptoolbox
tagline: Tools to help bring your project from an idea to a reality.
body:
### Welcome to Startup Gurus.
Startup Gurus is a team of students at the University of Ottawa who are committed to helping other students take their entrepreneurial projects from ideas to reality.

### Who are we?
Our team is comprised of Daryo Cummins, a business student, and Paul Laplante (@extraPaul), a computer science student.

![Daryo Cummins](https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/p/3/005/054/22c/302b12c.jpg) ![Paul LaPlante](https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAVkAAAAJGMzZjhlZDMwLTE5MmUtNDUxYy1hNDViLTE2NDFmMDg2NmM2Yg.jpg)
### Contact
For more information, answers to entrepreneurship related questions, or help with projects, please contact us at startupgurus123@gmail.com.
